246
00:17:52,680 --> 00:17:56,790
Xingyue sect is the evil path because it has made many evil things.

247
00:17:56,790 --> 00:17:58,560
Evil path?

248
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:03,650
Evil path, but it's the martial arts circle oath

249
00:18:03,650 --> 00:18:08,410
