253
00:18:24,600 --> 00:18:26,830
He was too powerful.

254
00:18:27,840 --> 00:18:31,960
Powerful enough to control the situation in the pugilist world.

255
00:18:32,610 --> 00:18:36,050
That kind of person, if unable to restrain,

256
00:18:36,050 --> 00:18:38,950
will let the safety of martial arts only between his thoughts.

257
00:18:40,450 --> 00:18:43,620
For Xiao Chun Hua, a hint is all that is needed.

258
00:18:45,730 --> 00:18:48,760
[Baxian Residence]

259
00:18:48,760 --> 00:18:51,370
- A prescription precisely? 
 - Yes.

260
00:18:51,370 --> 00:18:55,310
The Young Chief Master went back for the past two days and he is either talking nonsense or beating up.

261
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:58,240
So the two ladies are terrified.

262
00:18:58,300 --> 00:19:03,400
I thought about it and it would still be better to ask you to prescribe a dose of soothing soup.

263
00:19:05,450 --> 00:19:08,920
It's hard to say, the mind of this young man really changes unpredictably.

264
00:19:10,150 --> 00:19:13,540
Fortunately, I have seen a lot of people.

265
00:19:13,540 --> 00:19:16,450
I think you might back out.

266
00:19:16,450 --> 00:19:21,290
Just a moment ago, I specially made one with my own hands.

267
00:19:21,950 --> 00:19:23,590
Come!

268
00:19:30,380 --> 00:19:33,750
I can't thank you enough. I can't thank you enough for that!

269
00:19:34,750 --> 00:19:38,360
The Young Chief Master should be quiet, avoid movement, and shouldn't go out these days.

270
00:19:38,360 --> 00:19:40,560
Okay. Actually, the purpose of my visit today,

271
00:19:40,560 --> 00:19:45,090
is to personally request a prescription for a sedative soup from you.

272
00:19:50,560 --> 00:19:52,730
I have been negligent again.

273
00:19:52,730 --> 00:19:54,840
Not a problem.

274
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:20,570
They are all common medicines and shouldn't be too difficult to find.

275
00:20:21,600 --> 00:20:23,050
Thank you, Master Pu'er.

276
00:20:23,050 --> 00:20:27,850
- This... Young Master is still waiting for me, so I shall not disturb you further. 
 - Okay.

277
00:20:27,850 --> 00:20:30,410
- Goodbye. 
 - Please.

278
00:20:48,490 --> 00:20:50,860
At the ancestral hall of the Xiao residence,

279
00:20:50,860 --> 00:20:53,630
there is hidden a poem of remembrance.

280
00:20:53,630 --> 00:20:57,190
This shows Xiao Ming has not forgotten about his sworn brother.

281
00:20:57,190 --> 00:20:58,900
He doesn't even dare to write out his name!

282
00:20:58,900 --> 00:21:02,020
However, this has been the education of the Xiao family since long ago!

283
00:21:04,220 --> 00:21:08,060
It has been destined for this kind of guilt to be hidden in his heart.

284
00:21:08,920 --> 00:21:10,590
Education?

285
00:21:12,930 --> 00:21:15,290
Their so-called education

286
00:21:15,290 --> 00:21:18,390
is not the true difference between good and evil,

287
00:21:18,390 --> 00:21:22,780
but it is to prevent the status of the leader of the martial arts circle from crumbling.

288
00:21:22,780 --> 00:21:25,040
So is Xiao Bai.

289
00:21:30,890 --> 00:21:33,660
However, at least, they consider

290
00:21:33,660 --> 00:21:37,660
not harming innocent people when unnecessary.

291
00:21:39,880 --> 00:21:43,460
What about You Si and the youngest son of Nan Xinghe?

292
00:21:43,460 --> 00:21:47,300
Aren't they innocent or did they deserve to die?

293
00:21:49,550 --> 00:21:53,740
We have a chance to become an established sect,

294
00:21:53,740 --> 00:21:56,040
but they won't give us that chance.

295
00:22:00,590 --> 00:22:02,740
Shangguan Qiuyue,

296
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:07,660
but your methods

297
00:22:08,450 --> 00:22:11,390
are even more cruel and merciless.

298
00:22:17,540 --> 00:22:20,080
You hate my methods,

299
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:23,420
hate the fact that I have used you before,

300
00:22:25,030 --> 00:22:30,390
but Brother is doing this to make the pugilist world more organized.

301
00:22:33,410 --> 00:22:37,030
Xiao Chun Hua, you have said before

302
00:22:37,030 --> 00:22:39,710
that you wanted to live in carefreeness and stability,

303
00:22:39,710 --> 00:22:44,500
but in this martial arts circle that filled with conflicts,

304
00:22:45,460 --> 00:22:48,050
is there any true stability?

305
00:22:58,260 --> 00:23:00,970
So, you mean,

306
00:23:01,890 --> 00:23:07,270
designing a ploy to take advantage of me was all for my own good?

307
00:23:10,860 --> 00:23:15,090
When I finally rule all of the pugilist world,

308
00:23:15,990 --> 00:23:18,740
you will understand my intentions.

309
00:23:18,740 --> 00:23:21,890
You're not even able to make people believe you now,

310
00:23:22,770 --> 00:23:24,980
why are you talking about the future?

311
00:23:28,230 --> 00:23:31,980
I will listen to your words.

312
00:23:32,930 --> 00:23:35,670
I will also correct myself slowly in the future.

313
00:23:39,440 --> 00:23:44,200
I am no longer of any use to you.

314
00:23:46,580 --> 00:23:48,730
You also don't have to listen to me.

315
00:23:57,830 --> 00:24:00,610
If you still hate me,

316
00:24:02,460 --> 00:24:04,950
you can also take advantage of me.

317
00:24:04,950 --> 00:24:07,610
Take advantage of me to protect you for your whole life.

318
00:24:08,810 --> 00:24:11,640
In the future, any of Xiao Chun Hua's requests,

319
00:24:12,510 --> 00:24:14,850
I will fulfill them.

320
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:20,390
Really?

321
00:24:23,340 --> 00:24:25,370
I have said before.

322
00:24:26,460 --> 00:24:29,020
I will be good to you for your whole life.

323
00:24:39,080 --> 00:24:40,700
Okay.

324
00:24:44,330 --> 00:24:46,570
Older Brother, just let me go.

325
00:24:49,200 --> 00:24:51,960
This is my only request for you.

326
00:25:06,840 --> 00:25:10,040
Young Chief Master still cares for Miss Chun Hua.

327
00:25:10,040 --> 00:25:15,290
His illness immediately recurred when he heard about her crisis.

328
00:25:15,290 --> 00:25:19,020
Shangguan Qiuyue is scheming and unscrupulous, but we never would have thought.

329
00:25:19,020 --> 00:25:23,210
We never would have thought that Shangguan Qiuyue would make trouble at this time!

330
00:25:23,210 --> 00:25:26,190
He might just be afraid that our relationship with Master Shi has deepened by one step,

331
00:25:26,190 --> 00:25:29,570
so he let out the news of him being injured to confuse us.

332
00:25:30,360 --> 00:25:34,400
In the end, it gave Young Chief Master a heavy blow.

333
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:37,760
But how has he guessed that Young Chief Master would go crazy?

334
00:25:37,760 --> 00:25:41,720
That might not be the case! The last time when Fu Lou went to get the Longevity fruit,

335
00:25:41,720 --> 00:25:45,840
Shangguan Qiuyue openly sowed discord between Young Chief Master and Miss Chun Hua.

336
00:25:45,840 --> 00:25:48,600
It is evident that this person is very manipulative.

337
00:25:48,600 --> 00:25:50,760
He has done many deals for others before,

338
00:25:50,760 --> 00:25:54,980
so he should know Young Chief Master like the back of his hand.

339
00:25:54,980 --> 00:25:58,430
This devil is always hiding in darkness,

340
00:25:58,430 --> 00:26:01,580
watching how we fall into his trap.

341
00:26:01,580 --> 00:26:04,950
When the time is ripe, he will slowly reveal himself,

342
00:26:04,950 --> 00:26:08,180
and tease mercilessly.

343
00:26:08,180 --> 00:26:11,130
- Thus, it's the more that we must not fall into his trap. 
 - Yes.

344
00:26:11,130 --> 00:26:15,790
The immediate matter now is to find Master Shi and let the truth come to light.

345
00:26:21,010 --> 00:26:24,320
How about this? I will visit the Baxian Residence again.

346
00:26:51,280 --> 00:26:55,300
Xiao Chun Hua, you will regret this.

347
00:26:57,040 --> 00:26:59,280
Are you threatening me?

348
00:27:00,600 --> 00:27:03,100
From now on, no one will be there to protect you.

349
00:27:03,100 --> 00:27:05,050
I don't need anyone to.

350
00:27:07,120 --> 00:27:10,040
I can live well on my own.

351
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:15,190
This world is very dangerous,

352
00:27:15,190 --> 00:27:18,080
the kinder you are, the worse an outcome you will have.

353
00:27:22,360 --> 00:27:27,970
After leaving Qianyue Cave, I will have no ties to Qianyue Cave from now on.

354
00:27:28,750 --> 00:27:30,930
I will not frame you,

355
00:27:32,360 --> 00:27:35,780
and I hope in the future you also will not use me for your ploys.

356
00:27:38,780 --> 00:27:40,370
Okay.

357
00:27:44,610 --> 00:27:46,580
I promise you.

358
00:27:55,040 --> 00:27:56,800
Little Yan!

359
00:27:57,850 --> 00:28:01,310
Gu Wan? Why are you here?

360
00:28:03,210 --> 00:28:05,800
Did you forget what I told you?

361
00:28:05,800 --> 00:28:09,500
Every word you said, I remember it all very clearly.

362
00:28:09,500 --> 00:28:11,540
It's good if you remember it well.

363
00:28:11,540 --> 00:28:14,860
-  Do you think I will show you mercy? 
 - You won't!

364
00:28:15,430 --> 00:28:17,960
Hence, I specially came to see you.

365
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:21,300
It's because I already have finished the matter I should do.

366
00:28:22,250 --> 00:28:24,290
A matter you should do?

367
00:28:25,950 --> 00:28:29,050
I removed a thorny eye for you.

368
00:28:29,670 --> 00:28:31,640
What have you done?

369
00:28:32,230 --> 00:28:34,570
Answer me! What have you done?

370
00:28:38,290 --> 00:28:40,410
You will know very soon.

371
00:28:40,410 --> 00:28:44,720
Little Yan, you will thank me

